show.description:
Unbeknownst to him, Anastasiya is the sole heir of the famous AS Group.
She has three brothers – one of whom loves her more than his own life!
This is a story of love, betrayal, and the bonds of family – an emotional rollercoaster soaked in tears.
Listen now!
